{"tid":1291494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵即時停售今日中午起至晚上服務結束的所有高鐵車票","createTime":"2019-07-07T02:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T06:23:50.000Z","uid":41404,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f3285af4053b7147420bbdfbc7b557afd9db51b3","tid":1291494,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:20:08.000Z","msg":"港鐵表示，因應今日在香港西九龍站附近有公眾活動進行，預計有大量人流，加上西九龍站有特別安排，包括在一個指定入口讓乘客進入車站，及一個指定出口供乘客離開車站。在這情況下，為確保車站和高鐵列車服務運作暢順，票務方面實施特別安排，所有售票渠道，即時停止售賣今天由中午起至晚上服務結束的所有南行及北行列車班次車票，以維持車站秩序。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵說，乘客亦可考慮改乘城際直通車、東鐵綫經羅湖或落馬洲口岸前往中國，或使用其他跨境交通工具。"},{"pid":"812349f202d0ec377f97e3b30d995e34cdc94c38","tid":1291494,"uid":191989,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:22:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fccae670748bf38bc3c077855babcf2e3070a43c","tid":1291494,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:23:27.000Z","msg":"本身已經無人搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要倒米"},{"pid":"0cd9f5839433c8309f1ddfe2410ab789dd3f6839","tid":1291494,"uid":71824,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fccae670748bf38bc3c077855babcf2e3070a43c","tid":1291494,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:23:27.000Z","msg":"本身已經無人搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要倒米"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:29:31.000Z","msg":"就黎cut直通車班次去谷高鐵啦"},{"pid":"fd3a9b05e2c940feebf4d70e6f8a3d861e9391f9","tid":1291494,"uid":15084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:33:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過多排就會話示威造成損失，傷害旅遊業<br />\n同當年928一樣"},{"pid":"8f8b9bb2bca78ed3df3d12f1a27779ee8828a13f","tid":1291494,"uid":8257,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0cd9f5839433c8309f1ddfe2410ab789dd3f6839","tid":1291494,"uid":71824,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fccae670748bf38bc3c077855babcf2e3070a43